data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER!  This spacious brick ranch located in Dublin has: NEW metal roof, NEW French Drain system, NEW fencing in front yard, NEW Stain-master Pet Protect Carpet, NEW Sump Pump. Heat Pump has had a recent HVAC System service/inspection. TWO Garages, with one Garage at the back of the house connecting to an enclosed 19 x 34 porch for year around enjoyment. Primary Bedroom with En-Suite Bathroom, 2 Additional Bedrooms, Hall Bathroom, Living Room, Kitchen and Laundry Room on main level. Multiple non-conforming rooms in basement that need additional finishing, but could be used as additional bedrooms, an office, or workout space, including a living room area with a fireplace. Lots of room for lots of possibilities! There is a canning room, and a pantry room for extra storage. Comcast Internet.  Just 3 miles from I81, and just off Rt 100, it is close to shopping, schools, Hospital, NRCC, Dublin Airport, and the NRV Fairgrounds, this home epitomizes comfort and convenience.
